pageContext.claim: “And I was truly proud to have [Polish American] support in the 2016 election.”
pageContext.analysis: While some people provide anecdotal evidence that suggests Trump enjoyed more support from Polish Americans, we found no correlation between the density of the Polish American population and the 2016 vote. It's even harder to say definitely that they had a higher turnout than in past years. The president is greatly exaggerating here.
